type.title: World Type
type.description: Control how visitors load into your world. Augment Worlds get ADDED to the regular parcel build. Holistic Worlds REPLACE the regular parcel build.

allowedParcels.title: Allowed Parcels
allowedParcels.description: Explicitly list which PARCEL IDs that Somnium Space Web is allowed to use this world on. Leave blank to allow ANY parcel to use this world.

url.title: URL
url.description: URL to bind to this entity's model.

thumbnail.title: UI Thumbnail
thumbnail.description: Appears in the menu when the user clicks on the object.

description.title: UI Text
description.description: Optional. The text to show on the menu when the user clicks on the object.

resolution.title: Resolution
resolution.description: Control the resolution scale of the web browser object.

autoPlay.title: AutoPlay
autoPlay.description: Automatically activates this web browser object upon spawning into the world.
